      <title>为什么我们做不好自动化测试？</title>
      <link>https://blog.xuh.me/posts/the-reasons-why-automated-testing-did-not-meet-expectations/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2020 10:00:21 +0800</pubDate>
